esh platform architecture links remote extraction networks with natural language routing layers. By leveraging Field Operations and Safety Knowledge Agents, extraction leads can fetch hazard reports and audit heavy machinery performance without latency or high bandwidth constraints.\\n 79 |           </p>\\n 80 |           <div className=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n 81 |             {[\\n 82 |               { id: \\\"gateway\\\", name: \\\"OREMesh Data Gateway\\\", desc: \\\"Aggregates edge machine diagnostics, haul-truck telemetry, and shift logs.\\\" },\\n 83 |               { id: \\\"orchestrator\\\", name: \\\"OREMesh Cognitive Router\\\", desc: \\\"Coordinates low-bandwidth natural language search and remote-site safety alerts.\\\" },\\n 84 |               { id: \\\"audit\\\", name: \\\"Site Operations Hub\\\", desc: \\\"Tracks daily geological grade reports, machinery upkeep orders, and hazard checklist logs.\\\" }\\n 85 |             ].map((tab) => (\\n 86 |               <button\\n 87 |                 key={tab.id}\\n 88 |                 onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab.id)}\\n 89 |                 className={`w-full p-3 rounded-xl text-left border text-xs transition-all ${\\n 90 |                   activeTab === tab.id ? \\\"bg-white/5 border-white/10 text-white\\\" : \\\"border-transparent text-white/50 hover:text-white\\\"\\n 91 |                 }`}\\n 92 |               >\\n 93 |                 <span className=\\\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\\\">{tab.name}</span>\\n 94 |                 {activeTab === tab.id && <p className=\\\"text-[11px] text-white/60 leading-normal font-light mt-1\\\">{tab.desc}</p>}\\n 95 |               </button>\\n 96 |             ))}\\n 97 |           </div>\\n 98 |         </div>\\n 99 | \\n100 |         {/* Interactive SVG Architecture */}\\n101 |         <div className=\\\"lg:col-span-7 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050507]/40 backdrop-blur-[12px] flex flex-col items-center\\\">\\n102 |           <span className