ors, fake dates, fake PDFs, or fake downloads. Use category cards, editorial visuals, research library previews, and coming-soon states. Design should feel like a premium research and intelligence library. Mobile friendly. Run lint/build.\\\"\\n 97 |   },\\n 98 |   {\\n 99 |     \\\"id\\\": \\\"12-blueprint-generator-compliance\\\",\\n100 |     \\\"title\\\": \\\"Verify and fix Blueprint Generator scoring\\\",\\n101 |     \\\"scope\\\": \\\"functionality\\\",\\n102 |     \\\"target\\\": \\\"Blueprint Generator\\\",\\n103 |     \\\"allowLandingChanges\\\": true,\\n104 |     \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Verify and fix the Blueprint Generator. It must be frontend-only and may appear on homepage and /build/blueprint. It must include title: Get Your Enterprise AI Blueprint in 60 Seconds. Required inputs: Industry, Company Size, Top Priorities with max 3 selection, AI Journey, Data Readiness, Leadership Commitment, Biggest Challenge, Email, OTP placeholder. Optional: Budget and Geography. It must not send real OTP or call backend. Formula: Blueprint Score = 0.20(AI Maturity)+0.25(Business Need)+0.20(Data Readiness)+0.20(Process Complexity)+0.15(Transformation Readiness). Scoring: No AI 10, Exploring AI 30, Running Pilots 60, Scaling AI 85, AI-Driven Enterprise or AI-Native 100. Business Need: Cost Reduction 20, Productivity 20, Customer Experience 15, Revenue Growth 15, Compliance 10, AI Transformation 20, Automate Processes 20, capped at 100. Data Readiness: Highly fragmented 20, Partially connected 50, Mostly integrated 75, Fully integrated 100. Process Complexity: <100 20, 100-1000 50, 1000-10000 80, 10000+ 100. Transformation Readiness: Not Discussed 20, Exploring 50, Budget Approved 80, Executive Mandate 100. Categories: 0-25 AI Beginner, 26-50 AI Explorer, 51-70 AI Adopter, 71-85 AI Transformer, 86-100 AI-Native Leader. Test example Banking, 15000 employees, Scaling AI, Productivity + Cost Reduction + Compliance, Mostly Integrated Data, Budget Approved must display 87/100. R