d)+0.20(Data Readiness)+0.20(Process Complexity)+0.15(Transformation Readiness). Scoring: No AI 10, Exploring AI 30, Running Pilots 60, Scaling AI 85, AI-Driven Enterprise or AI-Native 100. Business Need: Cost Reduction 20, Productivity 20, Customer Experience 15, Revenue Growth 15, Compliance 10, AI Transformation 20, Automate Processes 20, capped at 100. Data Readiness: Highly fragmented 20, Partially connected 50, Mostly integrated 75, Fully integrated 100. Process Complexity: <100 20, 100-1000 50, 1000-10000 80, 10000+ 100. Transformation Readiness: Not Discussed 20, Exploring 50, Budget Approved 80, Executive Mandate 100. Categories: 0-25 AI Beginner, 26-50 AI Explorer, 51-70 AI Adopter, 71-85 AI Transformer, 86-100 AI-Native Leader. Test example Banking, 15000 employees, Scaling AI, Productivity + Cost Reduction + Compliance, Mostly Integrated Data, Budget Approved must display 87/100. Required outputs: AI Readiness Score, Top 5 Recommended AI Opportunities, Recommended GFF AI Solution, Expected Business Impact, 90-Day Roadmap. Label impacts as expected/modelled, not guaranteed. Run lint/build.\\\"\\n105 |   },\\n106 |   {\\n107 |     \\\"id\\\": \\\"13-nav-footer-and-sitemap-completion\\\",\\n108 |     \\\"title\\\": \\\"Complete navigation footer and sitemap links\\\",\\n109 |     \\\"scope\\\": \\\"navigation-footer\\\",\\n110 |     \\\"target\\\": \\\"Header Footer Sitemap\\\",\\n111 |     \\\"allowLandingChanges\\\": false,\\n112 |     \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Verify and complete the public navigation, footer, and sitemap route links. Do not redesign header or footer. Keep the current approved visual style. Header must include HOME, WHY GFF AI, CAPABILITIES, INDUSTRIES, PLATFORMS, BUILD WITH GFF, RESOURCES, COMPANY, CONTACT, CLIENT LOGIN. Footer must include Quick Links, Solutions, Industries, Platforms, Company, Legal, Newsletter where current layout supports it. Required legal/support links: Privacy, NDA, Terms, Investor Relations, Client Portal. All hrefs m